有一扇窗户，窗户上方有木质窗框结构，窗户上装有灰色卷帘。天花板为白色吊顶，带有嵌入式灯具。\n\n【图片目的】\n展示当前截图内容\n\n【是否屋内设施照片】\n是\n\n【匹配商品】\n电热水器，毛巾架，墙面，窗户\n\n【是否对账图片】\n否\",\"aiType\":2,\"ruleHost\":\"http://rule.cloudkeeper.huiju.ke.com\",\"msgTime\":\"2026-06-30 10:44:27\",\"senderType\":4,\"inContractId\":4179761,\"resblockId\":\"3711100264079\",\"contractCode\":\"TGCF2606534989\",\"atList\":\"\"},\"answerGenerated\":false,\"require\":\"意图引导\",\"sessionId\":\"new_session_id:SERVICE_KEEPER--GROUP_CHAT--10941756792564918--4#1782785216000\",\"aiInvolve\":\"0\",\"picture\":\"\",\"intention\":\"意图引导\",\"businessScene\":2,\"firstTrigger\":0,\"answer\":\" \",\"senderType\":4,\"contractCode\":\"TGCF2606534989\",\"sessionInitiator\":5,\"matchingPlan\":\"GENERAL\",\"messageContent\":\"https://quan-picture-1259287960.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/1171/87a7fd93f24b46d0b45236146742e0e4.jpeg\"}",
